.Dd March 20, 2019
.Dt ASCENSION-BIND 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ascension-bind
.Nd Allows local zone transfer on bind for migration into GNS
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
This package modifies existing bind configuration to allow zone transfer to
localhost to allow the python3-ascension package to migrate the zone into GNS.
